==Usage instructions==
<pre><nowiki>
{{scroll box
|content=

}}
</nowiki></pre>

NOTE: An optional '''width''' variable can be used to control the width of the scroll box:
<pre><nowiki>
{{scroll box
|width=75%
|content=

}}
</nowiki></pre>

